{"tid":686772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【法庭影相】抱怨事件提升至國與國層面 唐琳玲：令我被污辱了","createTime":"2018-06-01T14:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T06:12:41.000Z","uid":38703,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2c88b33a82d7d622ea19b9e6eef155ec320eca","tid":686772,"uid":38703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"自稱央企高層的內地奇女子唐琳玲涉於高院法庭拍照並上載至微信，被控刑事藐視法庭，唐已自辯完畢並即席開始陳詞。她指案件本來只屬她個人拍照的事件，但卻被大狀艾勤賢利用，將事件變得更嚴重，「給我做律師代表，套取了我個人隱私，不正當發佈了給媒體」，又指案件現已上升至<span style=\"color: red;\">國家與國家</span>的層面，「令我被污辱了」，更指如果她拍照，能令相關部門重視，引起部門改革。唐最後感謝法官：「我相信法律是公正，法官是公正，給我一個公正的判決」。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉則指要時間準備寫判詞，將案押後至下周期一早上宣讀裁決，期間唐須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265187&d=iwrpB9Jvb375Ye5ZGadx1E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=198e9ee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265187&h=f010a977\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265187</a>  <br />\n<br />\n國家與國家的層面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f6acdec3f1a19760d5458dfebddcc29b0c165c","tid":686772,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"屌，原來自己友<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/194610_edfa05c5b4069d943386deac44093e8b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F194610_edfa05c5b4069d943386deac44093e8b.gif&h=5b7b71ac&s={SIZE}